cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.RO

The paper focuses on fruit detection and counting using deep learning approaches, which are commonly studied in the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of neural networks also falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. The paper also involves tracking fruits in images, which is related to robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the paper involves evaluating the performance of different methods, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
